                "callback_url_1": {
                  "description": "One of the three URLs where Transaction Broker will POST to when a HPP request is completed. This eliminates the need for polling for the request's status. Only HTTPS URLs are allowed. The callback will retry if the host is unresponsive. The response received from the callback url must have the response code 2xx. Basic auth credentials may be added in to url ie. 'https://username:password@address.com' or as an url param 'https://address.com?token=secret'. Size range - `0..2000`.",
